    "rowsha": "qwJ0dhua1ypoog+04KOpi0MIHXbME2HMudcS6nVugtQ=",
    "originContent": "I highly recommend using flatpak version, because, distro based wine (wine-staging) keeps on updating and games may break every few days. Using wine stable from flathub is better or use wine stable 5.0 or 7.0 from the distro packages.",
    "translatedContent": "Recomiendo encarecidamente usar la versión flatpak, porque el wine basado en la distro (wine-staging) se actualiza constantemente y los juegos pueden dejar de funcionar cada pocos días. Usar wine estable de flathub es mejor o usar wine estable 5.0 o 7.0 de los paquetes de la distro."
